org.iotivity.service.resourcecontainer

Interface RcsResourceContainerBundleAPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RcsResourceContainer

    public interface RcsResourceContainerBundleAPI
    This class provides APIs for managing the container and bundles in the container. The container provides such an interface to the bundle developer to access the configuration and to register/unregister resources.
